sub_title: Mindfulness Based Cognitive Therapist & Yoga Coach in training/Legal Biz Designer/Motivation Coach (ACC-ICF), Creative Healer and a Mom of two teens (sometimes one of the most demanding roles)
summary:
I am a slightly unconventional legal professional, innovation seeker, passionate about connecting legal, business, design and human interpersonal dynamics in one sustainable ecosystem.

As a change leader with 20+ years of experience in legal field, legal design and coaching I bring expertise which spans across the areas of:
✔️ GDPR proof digital contracts ✔️ business, contract & regulatory compliance  ✔️ negotiation  ✔️mediation ✔️risk management & mitigation ✔️legal & UX research ✔️ TM registration assistance ✔️executive & legal coaching: helping people unleash their brilliance ✔️customer experience support

Throughout my legal journey in advocacy, notary and corporate sector and later on in coaching and legal design I have been serving corporate and private clients in different legal and business areas by bridging sustainable business and legal solutions. Ongoing professional and personal development help me brush my legal and creative skills, alongside coaching mindset while maintaining high level of performance, work ethics and good sense of humor as integrated part of my daily work flow. 

BEING LEGAL & BUSINESS PROFESSIONAL IS NOT ALL I DO 
As a long time meditator, yoga practitioner, & organisational coach (ICF - ACC), I am enthusiastic about human well-being. Therefore, I have created the S.I.A.M. (Sail In A Moment) approach. S.I.A.M. stands for presence-based neuro-agile approach which helps business & legal minds, and everyday leaders to develop high level of mental & emotional awareness, motivation, engagement, productivity, satisfaction and achieve work-life balance.

PERSONAL NOTE 
I am adventurous and socially oriented person, passionate about travelling and diverse international settings ( 10 years of life abroad). I use my family time, yoga and sailing as my reset button.

Get in touch with me at morana@sailinamoment.com

My well-being website: https://www.sailinamoment.com/
